!!! v1.0.3 (2026-04-28)

* Fixed lazy-loading support for skinny tiddlers by triggering core lazy loading on hover
* Preview popups now also show for metadata-only tiddlers without a `text` field
* Removed the `exclude-empty` option because empty tiddlers should still preview their metadata

---

!!! v1.0.2 (2026-04-28)

* Migrated the startup module from JavaScript to TypeScript
* Kept the hover preview event delegation behavior unchanged

---

!!! v1.0.0 (2026-01-20)

Complete rewrite of the preview plugin.

Breaking changes:

* Removed dependencies on `tobibeer/appear` and `ooktech/dynamic-tables`
* Requires TiddlyWiki 5.2.0 or later
* Simplified configuration options

Technical improvements:

* Replaced widget hijacking with lightweight startup module
* Uses standard Reveal widget and PageTemplate
* Integrated with TiddlyWiki palette system for theme compatibility
* Modern CSS with backdrop-filter glass effect and smooth animations
* Document-level event delegation for better performance
* 150ms hover delay to avoid accidental triggers

File changes:

* Added: `startup.js`, `page-template.tid`, `palette-styles.tid`
* Modified: all style and template files
* Removed: `link.js`, `keyboard.js`, `popups.tid`

Migration:

Upgrading from 0.6.0 should work automatically. Custom templates remain compatible.

---

!!! v0.6.0 (2020-04-14)

* Fork of tobibeer/preview plugin
* Added auto-close on mouse leave
* Added glass effect styling